name: Trash Diver (Jetpack)
description:
#teamseas

This is a game made to spread awareness about our polluted seas. Team seas is a big gathering of creators to make creative projects about the trash in the ocean, and what we should do about it. 

This game was made in 48 hours in Construct 3. The music in the game is made by Icoso: https://www.youtube.com/c/Icosogames

You can also check out my YouTube channel: https://www.youtube.com/c/Jetpackyt

Thank you for playing my game :)
